\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {8}{\ignorespaces Runtime-memory Pareto plots for the exact active-edge solvers. The L1 panel compares the active-edge L1 operator with the full-pairwise L1 reference, and the L2 panel compares active-edge L2 augmented-design construction with the full-pairwise L2 reference. Left is faster, down is lower peak memory, and the lower-left quadrant indicates improvement on both efficiency axes.}}{23}{figure.8}\protected@file@percent }
